strings: <voice_0x010012BB><se_high>Accuracy: I jumped out to see if I could stop Dalmagus. Can he avenge Steer's death?
<voice_0x010012BC><se_high>Accuracy: However, it turns out that Domac is just a puppet, and the real villain is Lappthorne.
<voice_0x010012BD><se_high>Accuracy: Do you know how many times we've had an enemy like this...it just doesn't work...
<voice_0x010012BF><se_high>Accuracy: I don't know what has happened to me recently. I usually inspire others, don't I?
<voice_0x010012C1><se_high>Accuracy: You really think that? haha still pretty...
<voice_0x010012C4><se_high>Accuracy: We leave tomorrow morning. i wanna sleep
<voice_0x010012C6><se_high>Accuracy: I promise to come back when I'm done with my errands.
